.Microcontrollers

1.STM32F407VGT6

ARM Cortex-M4 based 32-bit microcontroller

Used for sensor interfacing, data processing, and CAN communication

2.ESP32

Dual-core microcontroller with built-in Wi-Fi

Used as CAN-to-Cloud gateway and LCD controller

.Sensors

1.LM35 Temperature Sensor

Measures engine temperature

Provides analog voltage proportional to temperature

2.ADXL345 Accelerometer

3-axis MEMS accelerometer

Used to detect engine vibration and abnormal conditions

3.HC-SR04 Ultrasonic Sensor

Used to measure fuel level in the vehicle tank

4.Touch Sensor (HW-763)

Detects driver touch or safety input

.Communication Modules

1.MCP2551 CAN Transceiver (2 units)

Enables CAN communication between STM32 and ESP32

Converts CAN controller signals to differential CAN bus levels

.Connectivity & Prototyping

1.CAN Bus Wires (CANH, CANL)

2.Jumper Wires

3.Breadboard / PCB

4.Pin Headers & Connectors

